title: Le Dolly's
typeOfFood: Lacto, Indian, Beer/Wine, British, English, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Cozy English restaurant offering some vegetarian dishes, especially Indian ones. Chef/owner was previously a vegan chef. Could ask to make a dish vegan. Breakfast and lunch is offered til 2:30pm, then snacks til 7pm, then after which is dinner.
